      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable project or a budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dings consistent with its age, and the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts and drives, but the engine idle is slightly rough and the tires will likely need replacement within the next few months. All major electronics are functional, though some interior trim pieces are loose; it's a solid car for the price if you don't mind the cosmetic and minor mechanical needs.",
