    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to look at my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my reliable companion for years, and honestly, she still turns heads at every stoplight. She\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still having plenty of adventures left in her. You might find a tiny scratch here or there\u2014nothing that a bit of character doesn't explain\u2014but under the hood, she\u2019s as smooth as a summer breeze. I\u2019ve kept her clean and treated her right, and I\u2019m just looking for someone who will enjoy those weekend drives as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
