    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is a meticulously sorted driver\u2019s machine, optimized for those who value mechanical transparency and chassis feedback. The powertrain is exceptionally responsive, featuring a linear torque curve and a gearbox with tight, positive engagement and zero synchro grind. I\u2019ve addressed the common weak points in the cooling system and refreshed the suspension bushings to ensure the geometry remains true under heavy lateral load. The engine exhibits healthy compression across all cylinders, and the throttle mapping provides a crisp, visceral connection to the pavement. While it has been driven as the engineers intended, the maintenance log is exhaustive, reflecting a commitment to preventative care over reactive repairs. This is a robust, high-performance platform ready for the enthusiast who demands more than just a stock experience.",
      "price": 38500.0,
